      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 546,
      "message": "Expressions like this can be simplified without the need in a local variable and assignments.\n\nif (filesScanned == null) {\n    return new HashSet<>();\n}\n\nreturn filesScanned;\n\nor even\n\nreturn filesScanner == null ? new HashSet<>() : filesScanner;",
